org.prebake.fs
Interface NonFileArtifact<T>

public interface NonFileArtifact<T>

An artifact derived from files that is not represented in the file-system itself, e.g. a tool definition, a product, or an edge in the dependency graph.

See Also:
FileVersioner.updateArtifact(org.prebake.fs.ArtifactAddresser, T, X, java.util.Collection, org.prebake.core.Hash)
